commit_message:
Conditional update support for model fields

Currently expected values of VO conditional update support
dict with keys as names of VO's model fields only:
{'id': volume_id}
With this patch conditional update will also support fields
from other models such as:
{models.Volume.id: volume_id} or {'Volume.id': volume_id}

Change-Id: Iecc7e6e1381ee297f00bcad57c849827c0c3f4fe

